name: DateAndTime_betweenTest
description: Unit tests for the DateAndTime.between method, which generates a timestamp between two given timestamps.

test_cases.name: testBetweenValidRange
test_cases.description: Tests the DateAndTime.between method with a valid range of timestamps.

test_cases.name: testBetweenEqualDates
test_cases.description: Tests the DateAndTime.between method with equal timestamps.

test_cases.name: testBetweenInvalidRange
test_cases.description: Tests the DateAndTime.between method with an invalid range of timestamps, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.
